title: Japanese Style Miso Aubergine on itsu Ramen'Noodles with Teriyaki Sauce, Pak Choi and Peanuts
description: Take your noodles to the next level with itsu ramen'noodles. These restaurant quality Japanese-style noodles are tossed together with crunchy veg in a sweet, sticky sauce & topped with an umami-packed miso roasted aubergine.
